high_descs: Move forward, then turn left and go to the wall, then turn right to go to the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug at the coffee maker.
Turn around, go forward, turn left to go to the stove, then look up at the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and heat it up, then take it out.
Turn around, move forward to the wall then turn right to go to the coffee maker.
Put the mug at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left then walk across the room head to the coffee maker
Pick up the mug on the coffee maker
Turn right then walk straight, turn left head to the microwave
Open the microwave heat the mug, take it out, close the microwave
Turn left walk forward then turn right facing the coffee maker
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mug on the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk across the kitchen, then turn to your right and go to the counter across from you, with the coffee maker on top.
Remove the coffee cup from the coffee maker.
Turn around and go to the half wall before the garbage can and turn left, then go across the kitchen to the microwave, above the stove.
Place the coffee cup inside the microwave, to the left of the egg already inside, heat it up, then remove the coffee cup from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, turn right at the wall, and go back to the coffee maker on the counter across from you.
Place the coffee cup back under the spout of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee cup in the coffee maker.
